data.description: This lovely Norfolk bungalow comes with all the updates you could want and all the charm of a classic home! Pay the mortgage with this mini duplex! Has apartment upstairs with own private access. Lots of updates in this 3 Bed/2 Bath bungalow. Newer kitchen, hardwood floors, tankless water heater, new HVAC in 2017, new moisture barrier in crawl 2021. Large detached garage with electrical. Downstairs has 2 bedrooms and upstairs has a large "primary suite" that includes its own living room and mini-split air conditioner.  Dogs can play in the fenced in backyard while you relax on the large front porch or work on your next project in the detached garage. Please allow 24 hour notice; tenants and pups on property.
